The opportunity to pitch to investors looking to make Seed Investment
Expert hands-on coaching to help selected companies to refine their pitch 
A platform to connect with relevant people from your industry and visionary investors   
Membership to the Connected Places Catapult’s SME Network for ongoing support  and opportunities
